  "text": "Feed-forward DNNs and RNNs are sometimes combined to leverage the benefits of both. In [CITATION_1] , a CNN was used as a preprocessing phase to an LSTM based on system calls, creating a feature extraction method that leverage the spatially local correlation in the system calls sequences.",
